"portal. Because these file formats are region-specific (e.g., :doc:`SEPA "
"<sepa_payments>` in Europe, :ref:`NACHA <l10n_us/nacha>` in the U.S., or the "
"global :ref:`ISO 20022 <accounting/sepa_payments/iso20022>` standard), "
"consult your country's :doc:`fiscal localization <../../"
"fiscal_localizations>` documentation to verify supported formats."
