"客戶對銀行\\ `實施指南\\ <https://www.europeanpaymentscouncil.eu/document-"
"library/implementation-guidelines/sepa-credit-transfer-customer-psp-"
"implementation>`_\\ 所要求的，可確保與銀行的相容性。"

