msgstr "稅率為**含稅**總額的百分比。"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:181
msgid ""
"If :guilabel:`Included in Price` is disabled, the computation "
"is :math:`\\text{tax amount} = \\text{sales price} \\times \\frac{\\text{tax "
"rate}}{1 - \\text{tax rate}}`."
