msgstr "將應稅基準金額或計算稅額的百分比，精確分配至多個賬戶及稅務網格。"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:None
msgid "Allocate tax amounts to the right accounts and tax grids"
msgstr "將稅額分配至正確的賬戶及稅項網格"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:290
msgid "**Based On**:"
msgstr "**基於** ："

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:292
