"票`\\ 、\\ :guilabel:`庫存轉移入庫發票`\\ 、\\ :guilabel:`庫存轉移出庫發票"
"`\\ 或\\ :guilabel:`海關發票`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avalara_portal.rst:119
