"並按一下\\ :guilabel:`新增`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:29
msgid ""
"Alternatively, it is possible to create a vendor bill from the Accounting "
"dashboard:"
msgstr "或者，也可以從會計 Dashboard 建立供應商帳單："

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:31
