#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:92
msgid ""
"The Brazilian localization package ensures compliance with Brazilian fiscal "
"and accounting regulations. It includes tools for managing taxes, fiscal "
"positions, reporting, and a predefined chart of accounts tailored to "
"Brazil’s standards."
msgstr ""
"巴西本地化套件確保符合巴西財稅與會計法規。該套件包含管理稅務、財務規則、報表"
"的工具，並提供符合巴西標準的預設帳目總表。"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:96
msgid ""
"The Brazilian localization package provides the following key features to "
"ensure compliance with local fiscal and accounting regulations:"
msgstr "巴西本地化套件提供以下核心功能以確保符合當地財稅與會計法規："

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:99
msgid ""
":ref:`Chart of accounts <localizations/brazil/chart-of-accounts>`: a "
"predefined structure tailored to Brazilian accounting standards"
msgstr ""
":ref:`帳目總表 <localizations/brazil/chart-of-accounts>`：符合巴西會計準則的"
"預設結構"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:101
msgid ""
":ref:`Taxes <localizations/brazil/taxes>`: pre-configured tax rates, "
"including standard VAT, zero-rated, and exempt options."
msgstr ""
":ref:`稅務 <localizations/brazil/taxes>`：預先設定的稅率，包括標準\\ VAT、零"
"稅率與免稅選項。"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:103
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:71
msgid ":doc:`Payroll </applications/hr/payroll>`"
msgstr ":doc:`薪酬管理 </applications/hr/payroll>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:104
msgid ":doc:`Reporting <../accounting/reporting>`"
msgstr ":doc:`../accounting/reporting`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:111
msgid ""
"In the :doc:`chart of accounts <../accounting/get_started/"
"chart_of_accounts>`, the accounts are mapped automatically to their "
"corresponding taxes, and the default account payable and account receivable "
"fields."
msgstr ""
"在\\ :doc:`帳目總表 <../accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts>`\\ 中，帳戶"
"會自動對應至相應的稅務項目、預設的應付帳款與應收帳款欄位。"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:116
msgid ""
"The Brazil chart of accounts is based on the SPED CoA, which provides a "
"baseline of the necessary accounts."
msgstr "巴西帳目總表基於 SPED CoA，提供必要帳戶的基準。"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:124
msgid ""
":doc:`Taxes <../accounting/taxes>` are automatically created and configured "
"when installing the Brazilian localization. Avalara uses some to compute "
"taxes on sales orders or invoices."
msgstr ""
"安裝巴西本地化時會自動建立並配置\\ :doc:`稅捐 <../accounting/taxes>`\\ 。"
"Avalara 使用其中一些來計算銷售訂單或發票的稅額。"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:127
msgid ""
"Taxes used for services must be manually added and configured, as the rate "
"may differ depending on the city where the service is offered."
msgstr "服務稅捐必須手動加入並配置，因為稅率可能因提供服務的城市而異。"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:131
msgid ""
"NFS-e can't be issued for service taxes created manually. "
"To :ref:`electronically send an NFS-e <localizations/brazil/e-invoice-"
"services>`, compute taxes using Avalara."
msgstr ""
"無法為手動建立的服務稅捐開立 NFS-e。若要\\ :ref:`以電子方式傳送 NFS-e "
"<localizations/brazil/e-invoice-services>`\\ ，請使用 Avalara 計算稅額。"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:135
msgid ""
"Do not delete taxes, as they are used for the AvaTax tax computation. If "
"deleted, Odoo creates them again when used in an |SO| or invoice, computing "
"taxes with AvaTax. However, the account used to register the tax must be "
"reconfigured in the tax's :guilabel:`Definition` tab, under "
"the :guilabel:`Distribution for invoices` and :guilabel:`Distribution for "
"refunds` sections."
msgstr ""
"請勿刪除稅捐，因為它們用於 AvaTax 稅額計算。如果刪除，Odoo 會在\\ |SO|\\ 或發"
"票中使用時再次建立它們，並使用 AvaTax 計算稅額。但是，必須在稅捐的\\ "
":guilabel:`定義`\\ 分頁中，於\\ :guilabel:`發票分配`\\ 和\\ :guilabel:`退款分"
"配`\\ 區段下重新配置用於登記稅捐的帳戶。"

