msgstr "打印機點"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:169
msgid ""
"To configure your printer points, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Accounting: Journals`."
msgstr ""
"要配置打印機點，請轉到 :menuselection:`會計 --> 配置 --> 會計：日記賬`。"

