":guilabel:`Journal Name`: in this format `[Emission Entity]-[Emission Point] "
"[Document Type]`, for example: `001-001 Sales Documents`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`日記賬名稱`：格式為 `[發出實體]-[發出點] [文件類型]`，例如："
"`001-001 銷售文件`。"

