msgstr ""
"一旦所有\\ :ref:`配置 <peru-ecommerce-configuration>`\\ 設定完成，登入的客戶"
"在結帳過程中將可使用財務輸入欄位。"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:966
msgid ""
"When customers enter their fiscal data at checkout and complete a successful "
"purchase, the invoice is generated with the corresponding |EDI| elements. "
"The document type (Boleta/Factura) is selected based on their tax ID (RUC/"
"DNI). The invoice must then :ref:`be sent to the OSE and the SUNAT <peru-"
"electronic-invoice-status>`. By default, all published invoices are sent "
"once a day through a scheduled action, but you can also send each invoice "
"manually if needed."
msgstr ""
"當客戶在結帳時輸入其財務資料並成功完成購買後，發票將產生相應的\\ |EDI|\\ 元"
"素。文件類型（Boleta/Factura）根據其稅號（RUC/DNI）選擇。然後發票必須"
"\\ :ref:`傳送至 OSE 和 SUNAT <peru-electronic-invoice-status>`。預設情況下，"
"所有已發布的發票每天透過排程動作傳送一次，但您也可以根據需要手動傳送每張發"
"票。"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:972
msgid ""
"Once the invoice is validated with |SUNAT|, customers can download the .zip "
"file with the CDR, XML, and PDF files directly from the customer portal by "
"clicking the :guilabel:`Download` button."
msgstr ""
"一旦發票通過\\ |SUNAT|\\ 驗證，客戶可以直接從客戶門戶網站按一下\\ :guilabel:`"
"下載`\\ 按鈕，下載包含 CDR、XML 和 PDF 檔案的 .zip 檔案。"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:981
msgid "Permanent inventory reports: |PLE| 12.1 and |PLE| 13.1"
msgstr "永久庫存報告：\\ |PLE| 12.1 和\\ |PLE| 13.1"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:984
msgid ""
"Make sure to :ref:`set <peru/configuration-ple>` the appropriate type of "
"chart of accounts for your PLE reports."
msgstr ""
"請務必為您的 PLE 報表\\ :ref:`設定 <peru/configuration-ple>`\\ 適當的帳目總表"
"類型。"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:987
msgid ""
"Odoo can produce two permanent inventory reports as `.txt` files for "
"Peruvian accounting: |PLE| 12.1 and |PLE| 13.1. All inventory transactions "
"made need to be reported."
msgstr ""
"Odoo 可以為秘魯會計產生兩份 `.txt` 檔案格式的永久庫存報告：\\ |PLE| 12.1 和"
"\\ |PLE| 13.1。需要報告所有已進行的庫存交易。"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:990
msgid ""
"|PLE| 12.1 **only tracks inventory in physical units**, focusing on the "
"inflow and outflow of goods for effective management and planning."
msgstr ""
"|PLE| 12.1 **僅追蹤實物單位的庫存**，專注於商品的流入和流出，以實現有效的管理"
"和規劃。"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:993
msgid ""
"|PLE| 13.1 tracks **both physical quantities and monetary values of "
"inventory**, providing a comprehensive view for tax and management purposes."
msgstr ""
"|PLE| 13.1 追蹤**庫存的實物數量和貨幣價值**，為稅務和管理目的提供全面的視圖。"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:996
msgid ""
"Both reports must be maintained semi-annually (January-June and July-"
"December), with monthly transaction details reported within these periods. "
"The submission deadlines are October 1st for the first semester and April "
"1st for the second semester, in accordance with the *Resolución de "
"Superintendencia N° 169-2015*."
msgstr ""
"這兩份報告必須每半年維護一次（1 月至 6 月和 7 月至 12 月），並在這些期間內報"
"告每月交易明細。根據 *Resolución de Superintendencia N° 169-2015*，第一學期的"
"提交截止日期為 10 月 1 日，第二學期為 4 月 1 日。"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:1004
msgid ""
"Before generating the |PLE| 12.1 or |PLE| 13.1 reports, make sure "
"the :guilabel:`Peru - Stock Reports` (`l10n_pe_reports_stock`) module is "
"installed, then update the fields for:"
msgstr ""
"在產生\\ |PLE| 12.1 或\\ |PLE| 13.1 報告之前，請確保已安裝\\ :guilabel:`Peru "
"- Stock Reports`（`l10n_pe_reports_stock`）模組，然後更新以下欄位："

