"shipping_receiving/daily_operations>` include both incoming and outgoing "
"shipments."
msgstr ""
"轉移庫存是\\ |PLE|\\ 12.1 和\\ |PLE|\\ 13.1 報告中捕捉的關鍵流程。\\ :doc:`庫"
"存轉移 <../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"daily_operations>`\\ 包括進貨和出貨。"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:1052
msgid ""
