"Ogone must now be configured to accept payments from Odoo. Head "
"to :menuselection:`Configuration --> Technical Information --> Global "
"Security Parameters`, select :guilabel:`SHA-512` as :guilabel:`Hash "
"Algorithm` and :guilabel:`UTF-8` as :guilabel:`character encoding`. Then, go "
